.DT
set_turbidity
Disk World creator help
set_turbidity

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_turbidity -  This function is an alternative method of setting the clarity of the water.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_turbidity(int how_murky)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^how_murky%^RESET%^ - the new turbidity of the water
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/water.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is an alternative method of setting the clarity of the water.
The turbidity is defined as 100 minus the clarity of the water.  The default
turbidity is 10.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_clarity, query_turbidity

.EP

